{"tid":437671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國太空站「天宮一號」 約年底或明年初墜落","createTime":"2017-10-16T08:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T09:52:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8923e03767ca05e88e0f0bb2fe4c2bd5dbecc729","tid":437671,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/16/161144_37287c9bcbeda0d4aa58cc05f4dd633d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2F161144_37287c9bcbeda0d4aa58cc05f4dd633d.jpg&h=c81d3adb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕科學家近日透露，預計未來六個月內，重達8.5噸（約8500公斤），名為「天宮一號」的太空站將會墜毀地球，儘管大部分部件會被地球大氣層摧毀，但仍約有100公斤的殘塊可能會墜落地表。<br />\n<br />\n具《衛報》報導，哈佛大學天體物理學家，喬納森&middot;麥克道爾（Jonathan McDowell）表示：「目前天宮一號正接近地表約300公里，位於大氣層較濃厚的區域，太空站隨後的崩解速度也會越來越快，預計將會於2017年底，或2018年初墜落地面」。<br />\n<br />\n由於地球大氣層的變化，會讓預測著陸地點的誤差會超過數百英里，所以天宮一號殘骸的墜落地點難以預測。麥克道爾說：「出於無法預測天宮一號殘骸的墜落地點，我們也難以確定著陸的確切時間」。儘管預估太空站的殘片大部分會落在海洋中，但麥克道爾仍警告「可能會降下金屬碎片雨，或有人的車或屋頂被金屬碎片擊中，像飛機上掉落的殘片，但不會造成大規模傷害」。<br />\n<br />\n天宮一號自2011年由中國發射以來，一直用於載人和無人飛行任務。去年中國官方透露，天宮一號已超越預期服役時間，多了半年。中國在完成各項在軌試驗後，已終止和「天宮一號」的數據連接，太空站將進入地球大氣層燒毀。去年9月中，中國證實「天宮一號」將於2017年下半年墜入地球大氣層。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2222438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2222438&d=nBD%2B0oRb4ayqU%2FApFVeel3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d7da26ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2222438&h=d3b2a0ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2222438</a>"},{"pid":"7a8b7adcd6c756a6708ed0e2f764c2c200717a40","tid":437671,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2466018e2a455e5dd6238c9c4f90197c425bd6d1","tid":437671,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:15:47.000Z","msg":"我想問仲有冇其他太空站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69025b3b0417c3abba1c55700cb7307bf9720d8","tid":437671,"uid":75969,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"希望天宮一號可以順利回歸祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38930e8524795adaab7e817de66b3b683d59ad75","tid":437671,"uid":104443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"目標鎖定<br />\n北京：中南海"},{"pid":"3756f95296fd0f891903b9f9276a41e75dc4602e","tid":437671,"uid":34755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:20:53.000Z","msg":"殖民衛星降落作戰"},{"pid":"b14379589785f0d7eb63e038c5aa0f2821500c21","tid":437671,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:23:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問仲有冇其他太空站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國際太空站<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Space_station\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSpace_station&d=nBD%2B0oRb4ayqU%2FApFVeel3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=97be49cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Space_station</a>"},{"pid":"0256e681408cb08994c6b087b5c410ec59026f1f","tid":437671,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:27:03.000Z","msg":"天宮一號喜獲林鄭冚家接見"},{"pid":"f0ffbb4413893717edd4eae0f937eb7188931abb","tid":437671,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:28:05.000Z","msg":"炸落北京應該變世界危機<br />\n成千上萬蝗蟲衝去外國做難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af6e5e52ed5a897